<Q>Eorum qui impios Convertunt Nomina, ab Angelis <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span"> Judaei. <BIBL><HI>Grot.</HI> in <HI>Luc.</HI> 10. <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">.</BIBL></Q>
